{"tha-ap111:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap111:0.2":"Bhikkhadayivagga ","tha-ap111:0.3":"Bilalidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap111:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap111:1.2":"vasami pannasanthare; ","tha-ap111:1.3":"Ghasesu gedhamapanno, ","tha-ap111:1.4":"seyyasilo caham tada. ","tha-ap111:2.1":"Khanantalu kalambani, ","tha-ap111:2.2":"bilalitakkalani ca; ","tha-ap111:2.3":"Kolam bhallatakam billam, ","tha-ap111:2.4":"ahatva patiyaditam. ","tha-ap111:3.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap111:3.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap111:3.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap111:3.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap111:4.1":"Upagatam mahanagam, ","tha-ap111:4.2":"devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap111:4.3":"Bilalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap111:4.4":"pattamhi okirim aham. ","tha-ap111:5.1":"Paribhunji mahaviro, ","tha-ap111:5.2":"tosayanto mamam tada; ","tha-ap111:5.3":"Paribhunjitvana sabbannu, ","tha-ap111:5.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","tha-ap111:6.1":"‘Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap111:6.2":"bilalim me ada tuvam; ","tha-ap111:6.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap111:6.4":"duggatim nupapajjasi’. ","tha-ap111:7.1":"Carimam vattate mayham, ","tha-ap111:7.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap111:7.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap111:7.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap111:8.1":"Catupannasito kappe, ","tha-ap111:8.2":"sumekhaliyasavhayo; ","tha-ap111:8.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap111:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap111:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap111:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap111:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap111:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bilalidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap111:11.1":"Bilalidayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}